    "step-1": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "settings": {
        "subtitle": "Step 1",
        "heading": "Timber Selection & Treatment",
        "text": "<p>Every Aurowe product starts with carefully selected Nordic softwood. The timber is thermally modified at over 200°C — a chemical-free process that enhances dimensional stability, moisture resistance, and natural durability. Only timber that meets our grading standard moves forward.</p>",
        "button_text": "",
        "button_style": "primary",
        "heading_size": "medium",
        "text_size": "medium",
        "layout": "image_left",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "default",
        "padding_top": 60,
        "padding_bottom": 60
      }
    },
    "step-2": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "settings": {
        "subtitle": "Step 2",
        "heading": "Precision Milling & Joinery",
        "text": "<p>Treated timber is milled to precise tolerances using CNC equipment, then assembled by hand. Tongue-and-groove joinery ensures watertight construction without reliance on sealants. Every joint is inspected before the build moves to the next stage.</p>",
        "button_text": "",
        "button_style": "primary",
        "heading_size": "medium",
        "text_size": "medium",
        "layout": "image_right",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "surface",
        "padding_top": 60,
        "padding_bottom": 60
      }
    },
    "step-3": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "settings": {
        "subtitle": "Step 3",
        "heading": "Liner, Insulation & Systems",
        "text": "<p>Fiberglass liners are fitted by hand for a seamless interior finish. Closed-cell insulation is applied to retain heat efficiently. Heating systems, plumbing, jets, and filtration are integrated and pressure-tested to meet our performance standards.</p>",
        "button_text": "",
        "button_style": "primary",
        "heading_size": "medium",
        "text_size": "medium",
        "layout": "image_left",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "default",
        "padding_top": 60,
        "padding_bottom": 60
      }
    },
    "step-4": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "settings": {
        "subtitle": "Step 4",
        "heading": "Finishing & Quality Control",
        "text": "<p>Each product is sanded, oiled, and given a final visual and functional inspection. We test heating, water circulation, and structural integrity before anything leaves the workshop. The result is a product built to last decades, not seasons.</p>",
        "button_text": "",
        "button_style": "primary",
        "heading_size": "medium",
        "text_size": "medium",
        "layout": "image_right",
        "text_alignment": "left",
        "color_scheme": "surface",
        "padding_top": 60,
        "padding_bottom": 60
      }
